Notes: SP wins becomes fourth school to win two NCAA Division III championships,
having also won in 1987...SP is eighth school in Division III women's history
to win 30 games in a season...SP coach Shirley Egner's 200th career win...SP's
Boehning named tournament MVP...SP's Schmitt also on all tournament team.
Game.Officials: Jon Stigliano,  Todd Springer,  Darci Doll
